---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Mitt CV">
  <main>
    <!-- Centered Navbar at the top of the page -->
    <nav class="navbar">
      <div class="navbar-container">
        <!-- Navbar Buttons with Custom Styling -->
        <a href="/" class="navbar-link home-link">Home</a> <!-- Link to index.astro -->
        <a href="/cv" class="navbar-link projects-link">CV</a>
        <a href="/personligt-brev" class="navbar-link contact-link">Personal letter </a>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <h1 class="text-gradient">Mitt CV</h1>
    <!-- Border Box for CV Content -->
    <div class="box">
      <p>
        Jag har jobbat flera olika ställen sen jag var 15 år gammal. Jag började först som att jobba på fritids/dagis 
        från när jag var 15 till 17. Efter det fick jag sommarjobb hos Enerco inne på Sandviks industriområde och jobbade även där som timanställd ett tag innan 
        jag började på DHL, där jag nu arbetar extra medan jag studerar.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
  
  <style>
    /* Navbar container styling */
    .navbar {
      width: 100%;
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
      padding: 1rem;
      text-align: center;
      z-index: 1000;
    }

    .navbar-container {
      display: inline-flex;
      gap: 1.5rem; /* Space between links */
      justify-content: center;
    }

    /* Link styling */
    .navbar-link {
      text-decoration: none;
      background-color: transparent;
      color: white;
      padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 9999px; /* Rounded (pill shape) */
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease-in-out, color 0.3s ease-in-out;
    }

    /* Hover and active styles for each button */
    .home-link:hover {
      background-color: #ff0000; /* Red on hover */
      color: white;
    }
    
    .projects-link:hover {
      background-color: #ff008c; /* Pink on hover */
      color: white;
    }
    
    .contact-link:hover {
      background-color: #ff0000; /* Red on hover */
      color: white;
    }

    /* Heading and paragraph styling */
    h1 {
      text-decoration: underline;
      color: red;
      font-family: serif; 
      font-style: italic;
      font-weight: bolder;
      font-size: 5rem;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 5rem; /* Space below the navbar */
    }

    p {
      color: white;
      font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
      text-align: start;
      font-size: 20px;
    }

    /* Text gradient */
    .text-gradient {
      background: linear-gradient(187deg, red, rgb(255, 0, 144));
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    }

    /* Box styling */
    .box {
      margin: auto;
      width: 57rem;
      height: auto; /* Adjust height dynamically based on content */
      background-color: transparent;
      padding: 1rem;
      border: 1px solid white;
    }

    /* Basic reset and full-screen styling */
    *, *::before, *::after {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body, html {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-direction: column;
      background-color: #000;
    }
  </style>
</Layout>